NFS Share Manager v1.1.0
Build Date: $(date)
Platform: Linux x86_64
Qt Version: 6.x
KDE Frameworks: 6.x

Features:
- Local NFS share management with network accessibility
- Advanced network discovery with configurable scan modes
- Remote share discovery and mounting
- System tray integration
- Configuration persistence
- PolicyKit security integration
- User-configurable discovery timeouts and scan modes
- Comprehensive notification system
- Progress indication for operations
- Automatic local network configuration for shares

New in v1.1.0:
- Complete Scan mode for exhaustive network discovery
- Configurable scan mode parameters (timeout, max hosts, port scanning)
- Enhanced network discovery with proper subnet scanning
- Automatic local network access configuration for created shares
- User-configurable discovery timeout (30s - 5 minutes)
- Improved share creation with network accessibility
- Better progress reporting and scan statistics

System Requirements:
- Linux (Ubuntu/Debian/Fedora/Arch)
- Qt6 libraries
- KDE Frameworks 6
- NFS utilities (nfs-utils package)
- PolicyKit
- Network connectivity for discovery features